## Sprite License Notice

The sprite files included in this project are provided as examples and placeholders.
When using this project, please replace them with your own sprites or sprites
with appropriate licenses.

### Default Sprites
The SVG files in `assets/shimeji/` are created specifically for this project
and are released under the same MIT license.

### Third-party Sprites
If you use third-party sprites, please ensure you comply with their respective
licenses. Common licenses include:
- CC0 (Public Domain)
- CC BY (Attribution Required)
- CC BY-SA (Attribution + ShareAlike)
- MIT License

### Attribution
If you use sprites that require attribution, please include the attribution
in your project documentation or about section.
